            "team_handle": "torproject", 
            "message": "This does not seem like a security issue for me, given our threat model.\n\nOur services are not meant to protect users that don't use Tor, or that switch proxy to non-proxy. This is just a regular HTTP header like many servers around here.\n\nClosing this.", 
            "markdown_message": "<p>This does not seem like a security issue for me, given our threat model.</p>\n\n<p>Our services are not meant to protect users that don&#39;t use Tor, or that switch proxy to non-proxy. This is just a regular HTTP header like many servers around here.</p>\n\n<p>Closing this.</p>\n", 
